Macauhub is a free news service based in Macao, providing economic information in the Pan Pearl River Delta and Portuguese speaking countries in English, Chinese and portuguese. The Pan Pearl River Delta is located in the southern part of the people\'s Republic of China, including Hongkong, Macao, the surrounding eight provinces (Fujian, Jiangxi, Guangdong, Hainan, Hunan, Sichuan, Yunnan, Guizhou) and the autonomous region of.
